<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ف ل ع:</span> <span class="c2">(فَلَعَ)</span> الشَّيْءَ شَقَّهُ وَبَابُهُ قَطَعَ وَ <span class="c2">(فَلَّعَهُ)</span> أَيْضًا <span class="c2">(تَفْلِيعًا)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(تَفَلَّعَتْ)</span> قَدَمُهُ تَشَقَّقَتْ وَهِيَ <span class="c2">(الْفُلُوعُ)</span> وَاحِدُهَا <span class="c2">(فَلْعٌ)</span> بِفَتْحِ الْفَاءِ وَكَسْرِهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>